title: Mountain Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Beer/Wine, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This place makes an effort to provide for vegans. Has breakfast food, sandwiches, burgers, salads, and baked goods. Uses fresh, locally-sourced food with a New Zealand twist, served in the space above an outdoor gear shop. Vegan and gluten-free are indicated on the menu.
